938
00:59:49.961 --> 00:59:52.189
{\an8}<i>Ada yang terjadi, kan?</i>

939
00:59:52.213 --> 00:59:54.024
{\an8}<i>Tolong beritahu saya.</i>

940
00:59:54.048 --> 00:59:57.584
{\an8}<i>Kang-ho, ayo bermain.</i>

941
00:59:57.885 --> 01:00:01.297
{\an8}<i>Bagaimana kalau ini? Kami akan saling memberi hadiah.</i>

942
01:00:01.806 --> 01:00:03.284
{\an8}<i>Semuanya sia-sia!</i>

943
01:00:03.308 --> 01:00:04.910
{\an8}<i>Dia seorang jaksa.</i>

944
01:00:04.934 --> 01:00:07.871
{\an8}<i>Sayang, segera masukkan dia ke balik jeruji besi.</i>

945
01:00:07.895 --> 01:00:10.806
{\an8}<i>Mi-joo, aku tidak bisa menahan diri lagi.</i>

946
01:00:11.608 --> 01:00:14.435
{\an8}<i>Kang-ho seharusnya tetap mengetahuinya.</i>

